description:
This is Temple of Tezog, Also this is 7. 7 is lucky, 7 is also the number of times it took Beelzebub to fight against lucifer, to conquer the first 7 circles of hell. 7 is also the number of eyes of Tezog.

I have generated 71 different randomized fractals, some are beautiful and some are frightening to behold.

I will be releasing these weekly, as NFT's on different Blockchains, in sets of the greatest sequence of numbers that there is, Prime, until have released 67 onto markets.

There will be 4 NFT's that I have hidden through the web, and will be free to whoever can find them. I will be leaving clues to their whereabouts in some of my weekly posts on Instagram, and on the market description pages of previous uploaded fractals.
